verbose_text: The actions of Kruppel like factor 4 on non small cell lung cancer cell growth and aggressiveness were related to transforming growth factor-beta1-mediated ERK/JNK/NF-kappaB signaling [XREF_BIBR], and the novel human KRAB / C2H2 zinc finger protein ZNF418 suppressed MAPK signaling [XREF_BIBR].
evidence: zinc finger protein ZNF418 suppressed MAPK
